<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="64" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="5.[98,749,655,1002]" pageId="5" pageNumber="64">
<emphasis box="[136,360,655,679]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="64">Conservation status.</emphasis>
– Due to the apparent endemic distribution of 
<emphasis box="[224,435,688,712]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="64">
<taxonomicName authorityName="L. Kollmann &amp; Peixoto. A. Habit" authorityYear="2012" box="[224,427,688,712]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Begoniaceae" genus="Begonia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Cucurbitales" pageId="5" pageNumber="64" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="wasshauseniana">B. wasshauseniana</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
with extent of the occurrence estimated to be less than 
<quantity box="[365,432,721,745]" metricMagnitude="4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="64" unit="km" value="10.0">10 km</quantity>
<superScript attach="left" box="[432,440,720,734]" fontSize="6" pageId="5" pageNumber="64">2</superScript>
, habitat severely fragmented and continuing decline of the area, extent and quality of habitat, it seems prudent to include this species in the Critically Endangered species list (CR) (B2ab(iii)) according to the criteria of the 
<bibRefCitation author="IUCN" box="[220,363,852,876]" pageId="5" pageNumber="64" refId="ref3667" refString="IUCN (2001). IUCN Red List Categories and Criteria: Version 3. 1. IUCN Species Survival Commission." type="book" year="2001">IUCN (2001)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
